description:

description:
A staff passed down from royalty. It is said to empower

name: Princess Staff

description:

is, however, made from scratch.

description:
A dagger meant to use for practice, yet it can cause

name: Child's Dagger

description:
A bow which is made of fine wood. It looks worn
but overall is in good shape.
name: Bandit's Bow
